          "data": {
            "html": "<p>The most important part of the work plan is your objectives.</p><p><strong>Key aspects of your objectives:</strong> They provide the framework for all stakeholders on what you want to accomplish. They should be agreed upon by all stakeholders. They recognize the capacity of your organization.</p>",
